cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image classification tasks. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as it proposes a new classification algorithm. Multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories are also possible as the proposed method can be applied to various visual classification tasks.
